WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:04.328
[A new start! We will grow with you
at this new starting point]

00:00:28.254 --> 00:00:29.816
Yu Lei's not here.

00:00:29.816 --> 00:00:32.359
He should be back with Chen Ke.

00:00:32.359 --> 00:00:35.119
Who said I was looking for Yu Lei?

00:00:35.119 --> 00:00:37.080
Then you're here to...

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:40.280
For me?

00:00:40.280 --> 00:00:42.240
No way.

00:00:42.240 --> 00:00:44.079
Last time we played ball,

00:00:44.079 --> 00:00:45.640
you said my ball was old and dirty.

00:00:45.640 --> 00:00:47.079
So I went out and bought a new one.

00:00:47.079 --> 00:00:49.000
I didn't expect that you'd also...

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:51.039
I already told you, it's not for you.

00:00:51.039 --> 00:00:52.520
Don't get so close.

00:00:52.520 --> 00:00:54.600
You stink.

00:00:54.600 --> 00:00:56.074
What?

00:00:57.359 --> 00:00:59.079
Me? I just took a shower.

00:00:59.079 --> 00:01:00.799
How... How do I stink?

00:01:00.799 --> 00:01:02.159
I even put on some cologne.

00:01:02.159 --> 00:01:03.738
Smell.

00:01:05.879 --> 00:01:09.519
Since when did the big ape start
caring about his hygiene?

00:01:09.519 --> 00:01:13.679
Well... I wanted to change my image a bit.

00:01:14.920 --> 00:01:16.799
What happened to your hair?

00:01:16.799 --> 00:01:17.879
It's back to normal.

00:01:17.879 --> 00:01:18.959
Oh, this?

00:01:18.959 --> 00:01:20.159
My hair is naturally curly.

00:01:20.159 --> 00:01:21.840
Straightening it is too much work.

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:24.200
So I just left it like this.

00:01:24.200 --> 00:01:26.079
It's nice.

00:01:26.079 --> 00:01:30.222
You look better... the way you were before.

00:03:38.879 --> 00:03:41.757
[Episode 7: I Didn't Do Anything Wrong]

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:44.879
For this semester's final exams,

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:47.759
He Jin got the first-class scholarship
all to himself.

00:03:47.759 --> 00:03:49.479
If Yu Lei and Chen Ke had been here,

00:03:49.479 --> 00:03:51.062
he wouldn't have stood a chance.

00:03:53.680 --> 00:03:56.000
By the way, the counselor said

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:57.800
the scholarship money
will be distributed on Monday.

00:03:57.800 --> 00:03:59.599
Let's go out for a big meal then.

00:03:59.599 --> 00:04:02.195
Sounds good.
Let's go to that place by the school gate.

00:04:03.085 --> 00:04:04.840
Everyone's pretty busy
at the start of the semester.

00:04:04.840 --> 00:04:06.159
Let's talk about it when we have time.

00:04:06.159 --> 00:04:08.120
Right. No rush.

00:04:08.120 --> 00:04:11.520
- Yeah. That's true.
- Chen Ke. You're back.

00:04:11.520 --> 00:04:13.240
How's everything at home?

00:04:13.240 --> 00:04:14.504
- It's fine.
- You're finally back.

00:04:14.504 --> 00:04:16.439
We missed you like crazy.

00:04:17.399 --> 00:04:19.759
Don't touch it. I'll get it.

00:04:19.759 --> 00:04:21.360
Come on, come on, come on.

00:04:21.360 --> 00:04:23.800
We've already tidied all this up for you.

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:26.040
- Your little notebook, your bedsheets...
- We didn't even throw out your notebook.

00:04:26.040 --> 00:04:27.259
- Thanks.
- We even watered your plants.

00:04:27.259 --> 00:04:28.800
You don't have to clean anything.

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:30.579
We took care of it all for you.

00:04:38.680 --> 00:04:40.040
You guys...

00:04:40.040 --> 00:04:42.141
Yu Lei. When did you get back?

00:04:46.600 --> 00:04:49.439
You two... When did you get so close?

00:04:51.560 --> 00:04:53.193
So...

00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:57.319
Are you two now...
in "that" kind of relationship?

00:04:57.319 --> 00:04:58.519
We...

00:04:58.519 --> 00:05:01.240
Right now, not yet.

00:05:01.240 --> 00:05:04.800
But we're planning on giving it a try.

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:06.560
Who said I wanted to give it a try with you?

00:05:06.560 --> 00:05:08.276
Did you even ask me?

00:05:08.276 --> 00:05:09.800
Then let me ask you right now...

00:05:09.800 --> 00:05:12.920
Ouyang, will you?

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:15.319
Who told you to ask right now?

00:05:15.319 --> 00:05:17.879
Then I'll ask again tomorrow.

00:05:18.839 --> 00:05:19.879
No.

00:05:19.879 --> 00:05:21.519
- The day after tomorrow, then.
- No.

00:05:21.519 --> 00:05:23.639
Then when do you want me to ask?

00:05:23.639 --> 00:05:26.399
I'll ask whenever you want.

00:05:26.399 --> 00:05:27.925
Okay?

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:45.199
When did this happen?

00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:49.360
Maybe it started when, every morning,
I started to find doing my hair annoying.

00:05:49.360 --> 00:05:51.160
Things changed.

00:05:52.766 --> 00:05:55.086
Curly hair suits you better anyway.

00:05:55.990 --> 00:05:57.770
Tell me something I don't know.

00:05:59.279 --> 00:06:00.519
Ouyang Han.

00:06:00.519 --> 00:06:01.920
Seriously.

00:06:01.920 --> 00:06:05.480
No matter who it is,
as long as you truly like them,

00:06:05.480 --> 00:06:07.839
and that person can make you feel happy,

00:06:07.839 --> 00:06:10.560
I'll be happy for you.

00:06:10.560 --> 00:06:13.040
Besides, that guy Li Ming...

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:15.600
he only seems a little unreliable.

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:17.000
It just seems that way.

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:19.680
- He's actually a really good guy.
- Alright, alright, alright.

00:06:19.680 --> 00:06:22.759
How did one break from school
turn you into such a busybody?

00:06:22.759 --> 00:06:24.959
You should worry more about yourself.

00:06:24.959 --> 00:06:27.046
How are things with you and Chen Ke?

00:06:27.046 --> 00:06:30.240
You and Chen Ke...
have you made any progress?

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:31.839
What progress?

00:06:31.839 --> 00:06:33.439
What's there to progress?

00:06:33.439 --> 00:06:36.879
Chen Ke and I are just like blood Yu Leis.

00:06:36.879 --> 00:06:39.879
I think you're the one
who's dense as a block of wood.

00:06:39.879 --> 00:06:41.959
Your relationship with Chen Ke...

00:06:41.959 --> 00:06:44.400
is it really that simple?

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:54.210
What's not simple about it?

00:06:55.720 --> 00:06:57.600
Let me ask you this.

00:06:57.600 --> 00:07:01.000
When he's happy, are you happy too?

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:04.439
When he's sad, are you sad too?

00:07:05.160 --> 00:07:07.240
Every day, when you think about seeing him,

00:07:07.240 --> 00:07:10.319
do you smile without even realizing it?

00:07:10.319 --> 00:07:13.879
Every day, when you have to part ways,

00:07:13.879 --> 00:07:15.505
do you hate to see him go?

00:07:16.360 --> 00:07:18.079
When he's tired,

00:07:18.079 --> 00:07:20.680
do you want to be someone he can lean on?

00:07:20.680 --> 00:07:22.315
When you're feeling vulnerable,

00:07:22.315 --> 00:07:25.239
is he the first person you want comfort from?

00:07:26.759 --> 00:07:28.319
Do you want to kiss him?

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:29.800
Do you want to hold him?

00:07:29.800 --> 00:07:32.639
Do you want to chase away everyone
who shows interest in him?

00:07:32.639 --> 00:07:36.152
And never let him like anyone other than you?

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:41.520
He and I... W-We...

00:07:42.240 --> 00:07:45.439
When he's happy,
you're even happier than he is.

00:07:45.439 --> 00:07:49.079
When he's worried,
you're more anxious than he is.

00:07:49.079 --> 00:07:52.240
When he's troubled,
you're the first one to frown.

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:55.600
If that's not love, then what is?

00:07:56.680 --> 00:08:00.759
Yu Lei, you're in love with Chen Ke.

00:08:00.759 --> 00:08:03.319
Have you really not realized it until now?

00:08:46.039 --> 00:08:47.679
Yu Lei.

00:08:47.679 --> 00:08:49.034
Yu...

00:08:51.480 --> 00:08:52.840
What's wrong with you?

00:08:52.840 --> 00:08:54.480
You're totally out of it.

00:08:54.480 --> 00:08:56.329
I-It's nothing.

00:08:58.600 --> 00:09:00.759
Who was that text from just now?

00:09:00.759 --> 00:09:01.799
My mom.

00:09:01.799 --> 00:09:03.328
She sent a text, saying...

00:09:03.328 --> 00:09:05.759
On September 11th, 2001,

00:09:05.759 --> 00:09:08.440
there was a terrorist attack
in the United States.

00:09:08.440 --> 00:09:11.213
So far, 3,000 people have died,

00:09:11.213 --> 00:09:13.760
and over 6,000 are injured.

00:09:17.440 --> 00:09:19.720
How could so many people
be killed and injured?

00:09:19.720 --> 00:09:21.880
Life is just so unpredictable.

00:09:23.879 --> 00:09:25.799
Don't think about it too much.

00:09:25.799 --> 00:09:28.639
At least the two of us are still okay. Right?

00:09:28.639 --> 00:09:30.000
Yu Lei. Chen Ke.

00:09:30.000 --> 00:09:32.600
The counselor asked for you two
to find some time this afternoon

00:09:32.600 --> 00:09:33.919
to go see him in his office.

00:09:33.919 --> 00:09:35.759
What does he want with us?

00:09:35.759 --> 00:09:39.240
I think the results for
the make-up exam are out.

00:09:39.240 --> 00:09:41.720
- Oh.
- Okay.

00:09:41.720 --> 00:09:44.159
- Thanks.
- No problem.

00:09:44.159 --> 00:09:45.320
[Finance]

00:09:45.320 --> 00:09:46.677
Let's go.

00:09:51.480 --> 00:09:53.759
This is yours, Yu Lei.

00:09:53.759 --> 00:09:55.920
Here, Chen Ke.

00:09:57.679 --> 00:09:59.519
And you were worried
about your makeup exam.

00:09:59.519 --> 00:10:01.120
You did great, didn't you?

00:10:01.120 --> 00:10:02.679
You're the one who's amazing.

00:10:02.679 --> 00:10:04.559
I never see you studying.

00:10:04.559 --> 00:10:06.159
How are your scores so high?

00:10:06.159 --> 00:10:07.679
Yu Lei. Chen Ke.

00:10:07.679 --> 00:10:10.720
You two have always had excellent grades.

00:10:10.720 --> 00:10:13.120
I was never worried about you failing.

00:10:13.120 --> 00:10:15.312
But, Chen Ke,

00:10:15.312 --> 00:10:17.957
now that your family issues are all resolved,

00:10:17.957 --> 00:10:20.316
this semester, you need to settle down

00:10:20.316 --> 00:10:23.159
and put more focus on your studies.

00:10:23.159 --> 00:10:24.600
Ma'am, don't worry.

00:10:24.600 --> 00:10:25.679
Alright then.

00:10:25.679 --> 00:10:26.725
Because this semester,

00:10:26.725 --> 00:10:29.639
we're also paying close attention
to attendance.

00:10:29.639 --> 00:10:32.720
Even for our electives,
if you frequently miss class,

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:35.720
it will affect your overall credits.

00:10:35.720 --> 00:10:38.559
Ma'am, this semester,
Chen Ke and I took almost the same classes.

00:10:38.559 --> 00:10:40.039
We went to every single class.

00:10:40.039 --> 00:10:41.960
He wasn't absent.

00:10:41.960 --> 00:10:43.200
That's not possible.

00:10:43.200 --> 00:10:44.840
Several of his professors have reported to me

00:10:44.840 --> 00:10:47.120
that Chen Ke has been skipping class.

00:10:49.360 --> 00:10:51.800
Here. Take a look.

00:10:54.035 --> 00:10:55.480
Chen Ke, look.

00:10:55.480 --> 00:10:58.039
These classes are all marked as absences.

00:10:58.039 --> 00:10:59.600
That's impossible.

00:10:59.600 --> 00:11:01.679
I never signed up for these classes.

00:11:01.679 --> 00:11:03.679
Miss, this isn't my schedule.

00:11:03.679 --> 00:11:04.720
He's right, sir.

00:11:04.720 --> 00:11:06.399
Chen Ke and I
registered for classes together.

00:11:06.399 --> 00:11:08.120
I can vouch that he didn't pick these.

00:11:08.120 --> 00:11:09.399
That can't be right.

00:11:09.399 --> 00:11:11.559
Look, this is what the system shows.

00:11:11.559 --> 00:11:12.639
It's right here.

00:11:12.639 --> 00:11:14.544
And all the professors use this

00:11:14.544 --> 00:11:17.279
to track your attendance.

00:11:17.279 --> 00:11:19.240
Could it be a system glitch?

00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:22.519
Or, maybe there's been
some kind of mistake?

00:11:22.519 --> 00:11:24.639
Okay. Don't panic just yet.

00:11:24.639 --> 00:11:26.919
I will report this to the administration.

00:11:26.919 --> 00:11:30.520
Then, after I've verified the situation,
I'll let you know.

00:11:32.480 --> 00:11:37.039
History of Ming and Qing Law, Latin,
Greek Literature...

00:11:37.039 --> 00:11:38.600
What are these classes?

00:11:38.600 --> 00:11:40.480
I have no recollection of them at all.

00:11:40.480 --> 00:11:42.210
I know, right?

00:11:42.210 --> 00:11:44.320
They're all so obscure.

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:46.520
They sound painfully difficult.

00:11:47.480 --> 00:11:49.679
But we registered for our classes together.

00:11:49.679 --> 00:11:51.039
How could this have happened?

00:11:51.039 --> 00:11:52.360
It's impossible.

00:11:52.360 --> 00:11:54.879
We both chose our classes
on the computers in the lab

00:11:54.879 --> 00:11:56.440
and printed the schedules right away.

00:11:56.440 --> 00:11:58.159
If it were really a system error,

00:11:58.159 --> 00:12:01.256
then the ones affected
wouldn't just be me, right?

00:12:02.879 --> 00:12:05.919
Do you think it's possible
it wasn't the system?

00:12:05.919 --> 00:12:07.759
That someone secretly
logged into your account

00:12:07.759 --> 00:12:10.360
and changed your schedule?

00:12:10.360 --> 00:12:12.920
Who would log into my account?

00:12:13.919 --> 00:12:15.360
Maybe it was a hacker?

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:17.480
I heard it's super easy
for them to steal accounts.

00:12:17.480 --> 00:12:18.840
They have some kind of program for it.

00:12:18.840 --> 00:12:22.080
If it were a hacker, why wouldn't they steal
something more valuable?

00:12:22.080 --> 00:12:23.919
What do they gain by changing my schedule?

00:12:23.919 --> 00:12:25.120
It's not like there's money in it.

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:26.920
That's true.

00:12:28.480 --> 00:12:30.240
Why don't we go check the computer lab?

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:32.919
Maybe we can find some clues.

00:12:32.919 --> 00:12:35.138
- Okay.
- Let's go.

00:12:37.320 --> 00:12:40.120
Ma'am. This is really important.

00:12:40.120 --> 00:12:41.559
I'm begging you.

00:12:41.559 --> 00:12:43.080
But according to the regulations,

00:12:43.080 --> 00:12:44.720
you have to submit
a written application first.

00:12:44.720 --> 00:12:46.037
There's a procedure.

00:12:46.037 --> 00:12:48.360
It also needs to be signed off on
by the school's leadership.

00:12:48.360 --> 00:12:50.519
This matter is not my call to make.

00:12:50.519 --> 00:12:53.159
We just want to gather some evidence first.

00:12:53.159 --> 00:12:54.480
Please, could you bend the rules for us?

00:12:54.480 --> 00:12:57.279
The procedures and paperwork,
we'll complete them later. Is that okay?

00:12:57.279 --> 00:12:58.519
I'm really sorry.

00:12:58.519 --> 00:13:01.810
This matter, I really can't authorize.

00:13:03.960 --> 00:13:05.584
Damn...

00:13:08.159 --> 00:13:10.039
Ma'am, you have security cameras here.

00:13:10.039 --> 00:13:12.039
Can we review the footage from that day?

00:13:12.039 --> 00:13:14.120
We might find some evidence.

00:13:14.120 --> 00:13:16.759
But, if you want to access
the security footage,

00:13:16.759 --> 00:13:18.639
the police would have to get involved.

00:13:18.639 --> 00:13:19.919
Even the school administration might not...

00:13:19.919 --> 00:13:21.240
I'm begging you.

00:13:21.240 --> 00:13:22.991
Please.

00:13:25.039 --> 00:13:27.919
Ma'am, if your own child
were in a similar situation,

00:13:27.919 --> 00:13:31.741
you'd want to help them get justice,
wouldn't you?

00:13:32.639 --> 00:13:35.879
This incident happened several days ago.

00:13:35.879 --> 00:13:39.279
I can't guarantee the recording
from that day still exists.

00:13:39.279 --> 00:13:41.079
Thank you, ma'am.

00:13:54.519 --> 00:13:56.068
Found it.

00:14:15.320 --> 00:14:17.960
Ma'am, we've found the evidence.

00:14:17.960 --> 00:14:19.679
Yu Lei.

00:14:19.679 --> 00:14:21.062
Yu Lei.

00:14:21.799 --> 00:14:22.920
Yu Lei!

00:14:22.920 --> 00:14:25.265
- Where are you going?
- It has to be He Jin.

00:14:25.265 --> 00:14:26.360
I'm going to make him pay.

00:14:26.360 --> 00:14:28.080
Make him pay, how?

00:14:28.080 --> 00:14:30.030
He's the one who burned you before, right?

00:14:30.030 --> 00:14:31.720
This time he must be trying
to screw you over again.

00:14:31.720 --> 00:14:35.159
Even if you can let it go of this matter,
I can't.

00:14:35.159 --> 00:14:37.759
This time, I'm going to...

00:14:37.759 --> 00:14:40.279
- No. You can't go.
- Why not?

00:14:40.279 --> 00:14:42.639
With that scrawny body of his,
you think I can't take him on?

00:14:42.639 --> 00:14:44.241
Of course you can.

00:14:44.241 --> 00:14:47.759
But if you hit him,
you're the one who'll get in trouble.

00:14:47.759 --> 00:14:49.000
Bro.

00:14:49.000 --> 00:14:50.919
We can't just let He Jin get away with this.

00:14:50.919 --> 00:14:52.000
That's true.

00:14:52.000 --> 00:14:54.840
Then what do we do?
Just let him off the hook?

00:14:54.840 --> 00:14:57.360
Since we have evidence,

00:14:57.360 --> 00:14:59.159
how about...

00:14:59.159 --> 00:15:00.374
Come here.

00:15:07.679 --> 00:15:10.748
- What are you doing?
- He Jin. You're coming with me.

00:15:12.399 --> 00:15:14.759
Are you crazy?

00:15:14.759 --> 00:15:16.178
Let's go.

00:15:23.840 --> 00:15:25.759
What are you guys doing?

00:15:25.759 --> 00:15:26.960
Nothing much.

00:15:26.960 --> 00:15:28.519
We just want to have a little chat.

00:15:28.519 --> 00:15:30.799
What is there to talk about?
This is ridiculous.

00:15:30.799 --> 00:15:32.080
He Jin.

00:15:32.080 --> 00:15:34.879
My course schedule for this semester
was altered.

00:15:34.879 --> 00:15:36.399
Do you know anything about that?

00:15:36.399 --> 00:15:38.399
How would I know?

00:15:38.399 --> 00:15:40.559
Yu Lei and I both clearly remember

00:15:40.559 --> 00:15:42.320
that the last time we finalized our classes
this semester

00:15:42.320 --> 00:15:44.440
was in the library's computer lab.

00:15:44.440 --> 00:15:47.045
And, after we left,

00:15:47.045 --> 00:15:50.359
you were the one
who sat down at my computer.

00:15:51.600 --> 00:15:53.519
Why waste your breath on him?

00:15:53.519 --> 00:15:54.679
He Jin.

00:15:54.679 --> 00:15:56.879
You're the one who sabotaged Chen Ke,
aren't you?

00:15:56.879 --> 00:15:58.399
When he didn't log out of the system,

00:15:58.399 --> 00:16:00.440
you secretly changed his course selection.

00:16:00.440 --> 00:16:02.159
Do you have any proof?

00:16:02.159 --> 00:16:04.480
Don't make accusations without proof.

00:16:04.480 --> 00:16:06.679
Sure, I went to the computer lab.

00:16:06.679 --> 00:16:09.240
But I never touched the computer you used.

00:16:09.240 --> 00:16:11.759
Besides, it's been several days.

00:16:11.759 --> 00:16:13.840
Maybe you just remembered it wrongly.

00:16:13.840 --> 00:16:16.439
You're just trying to pin the blame on me.

00:16:21.241 --> 00:16:24.439
If you don't get out of my way,
I'm calling security.

00:16:25.279 --> 00:16:27.080
He Jin.

00:16:27.080 --> 00:16:30.639
Even now, you're still trying to deny it?

00:16:30.639 --> 00:16:32.559
I don't know if you've noticed,

00:16:32.559 --> 00:16:36.240
but the library's computer lab
has surveillance cameras.

00:16:37.799 --> 00:16:39.240
What does that have to do with me?

00:16:39.240 --> 00:16:41.399
I... I have a clear conscience.

00:16:41.399 --> 00:16:43.240
A clear conscience?

00:16:43.240 --> 00:16:45.960
Then do you dare come with us right now
and check the security footage?

00:16:45.960 --> 00:16:47.879
You're trying to trick me.

00:16:47.879 --> 00:16:49.040
Alright, Chen Ke.

00:16:49.040 --> 00:16:50.915
He won't confess
until he's faced with hard evidence.

00:16:50.915 --> 00:16:52.320
Once he sees himself committing
the act with his own eyes,

00:16:52.320 --> 00:16:53.679
he'll come clean.

00:16:53.679 --> 00:16:54.960
I get it now.

00:16:54.960 --> 00:16:57.159
You're just trying to pick
a fight with me, aren't you?

00:16:57.159 --> 00:16:58.840
Then hit me.

00:16:58.840 --> 00:17:01.120
Go on, hit me!

00:17:01.120 --> 00:17:02.879
That's enough.

00:17:02.879 --> 00:17:04.160
He Jin.

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:06.240
I don't want to blow this out of proportion.

00:17:06.240 --> 00:17:07.880
If you just admit your mistake,

00:17:07.880 --> 00:17:09.799
and explain the situation to the counselor,

00:17:09.799 --> 00:17:12.039
I'm sure they'll be lenient with you.

00:17:12.039 --> 00:17:14.359
Stop with the fake sympathy!

00:17:14.359 --> 00:17:16.720
Yeah. I did it all.

00:17:16.720 --> 00:17:18.559
So what?

00:17:18.559 --> 00:17:22.920
It's you people who look down on me,
one after another.

00:17:22.920 --> 00:17:24.440
You hate that I'm from a small town.

00:17:24.440 --> 00:17:26.599
You hate that I don't fit in.

00:17:26.599 --> 00:17:28.839
You laugh at me behind my back.

00:17:28.839 --> 00:17:31.279
What did I ever do wrong?

00:17:31.279 --> 00:17:34.440
I'm clearly more diligent than any of you.

00:17:34.440 --> 00:17:36.000
More self-disciplined.

00:17:36.000 --> 00:17:38.160
So how did I become
the one with the problem?

00:17:38.160 --> 00:17:39.759
He Jin.

00:17:39.759 --> 00:17:41.240
I've never thought that way.

00:17:41.240 --> 00:17:43.068
At Mingde University,

00:17:43.068 --> 00:17:45.595
everyone here was once
the top student at their school.

00:17:45.595 --> 00:17:47.480
No one here is better than anyone else.

00:17:47.480 --> 00:17:49.119
And no one is weaker, either.

00:17:49.119 --> 00:17:53.275
You can only earn others' respect
by acting with integrity.

00:17:53.275 --> 00:17:55.183
You blame everyone else for everything.

00:17:55.183 --> 00:17:58.040
Have you ever considered your own faults?

00:17:59.440 --> 00:18:01.279
Chen Ke, stop wasting your breath on him.

00:18:01.279 --> 00:18:02.559
Let's go straight to the counselor.

00:18:02.559 --> 00:18:04.064
Let's go.

00:18:08.680 --> 00:18:09.839
He Jin.

00:18:09.839 --> 00:18:13.079
Your actions this time
were indeed out of line.

00:18:13.079 --> 00:18:14.733
However, Chen Ke,

00:18:14.733 --> 00:18:17.920
your previous class schedule
really can't be changed back.

00:18:17.920 --> 00:18:19.000
How about this?

00:18:19.000 --> 00:18:21.480
I'll talk to the professors
and explain the situation.

00:18:21.480 --> 00:18:24.680
So your previous absences won't be counted.

00:18:25.680 --> 00:18:26.799
He Jin.

00:18:26.799 --> 00:18:27.720
After some discussion,

00:18:27.720 --> 00:18:29.412
and considering your usual
academic performance

00:18:29.412 --> 00:18:31.360
and grades have been excellent,

00:18:31.360 --> 00:18:34.298
and also because
you've admitted your mistake,

00:18:34.298 --> 00:18:37.160
the department will give you
a demerit on your record.

00:18:37.160 --> 00:18:40.839
However, this demerit will only be
sent to your parents.

00:18:40.839 --> 00:18:43.720
For now, it won't be publicly posted.

00:18:43.720 --> 00:18:47.000
Counselor, can you not tell my family?

00:18:47.000 --> 00:18:50.880
I... I was just trying to
play a prank on Chen Ke.

00:18:50.880 --> 00:18:53.880
If my parents find out, they'll kill me.

00:18:53.880 --> 00:18:55.079
That's not acceptable.

00:18:55.079 --> 00:18:57.799
This punishment is already very lenient.

00:18:57.799 --> 00:19:02.319
Also, you need to apologize
to Chen Ke in front of him.

00:19:03.839 --> 00:19:05.759
Chen Ke.

00:19:05.759 --> 00:19:07.302
I'm sorry.

00:19:16.959 --> 00:19:18.240
Ke Ke.

00:19:18.240 --> 00:19:20.680
Are you really planning
to move out of the dorms

00:19:20.680 --> 00:19:22.480
and never go back?

00:19:22.480 --> 00:19:24.039
Yeah.

00:19:24.039 --> 00:19:27.839
If I keep living there,
I don't know how I'd face He Jin.

00:19:30.400 --> 00:19:31.839
But you didn't do anything wrong.

00:19:31.839 --> 00:19:34.440
He's the one who should
be moving out, not you.

00:19:34.440 --> 00:19:36.920
No way. I can't just let this go.

00:19:36.920 --> 00:19:38.440
I'm not letting it go.

00:19:38.440 --> 00:19:40.240
I'm just tired.

00:19:43.071 --> 00:19:46.559
So, what's your plan now?

00:19:47.279 --> 00:19:49.079
Since the schedule can't be changed,

00:19:49.079 --> 00:19:51.079
I'll just take all the classes.

00:19:51.079 --> 00:19:53.280
I won't let him get what he wanted.

00:19:56.359 --> 00:19:57.519
It's getting late.

00:19:57.519 --> 00:19:59.400
Let's hurry up and pack.

00:19:59.400 --> 00:20:00.772
Okay.

00:20:11.840 --> 00:20:14.640
Come on. Don't think about
all that unhappy stuff.

00:20:14.640 --> 00:20:17.440
Let's celebrate your new place first.

00:20:17.440 --> 00:20:19.240
Thanks.

00:20:25.880 --> 00:20:27.536
Eat up, Ke Ke.

00:20:34.240 --> 00:20:37.079
I can't believe
you found a place so quickly this time.

00:20:37.079 --> 00:20:38.605
That's why I say, Ke Ke,

00:20:38.605 --> 00:20:41.920
you're just one of those people
who are blessed.

00:20:41.920 --> 00:20:45.119
Things will definitely
get better and better for you.

00:20:45.119 --> 00:20:46.919
Really?

00:20:48.240 --> 00:20:51.160
Well, of course it is.

00:20:51.160 --> 00:20:53.250
A-As long as we...

00:20:54.000 --> 00:20:58.319
As long... As long as we...

00:21:00.000 --> 00:21:02.399
Slow down.

00:21:04.830 --> 00:21:06.190
Yu Lei.

00:21:06.870 --> 00:21:08.880
Tell me, why?

00:21:08.880 --> 00:21:11.319
Even though I haven't done anything wrong,

00:21:11.319 --> 00:21:16.200
all this trouble always seems to find me.

00:21:17.480 --> 00:21:19.759
Could it be...

00:21:19.759 --> 00:21:21.960
that I'm really the problem?

00:21:25.039 --> 00:21:26.839
No. That's not it, Ke Ke.

00:21:26.839 --> 00:21:29.359
There's nothing wrong with you.

00:21:29.359 --> 00:21:30.359
Don't worry.

00:21:30.359 --> 00:21:31.720
Since you see me as a brother,

00:21:31.720 --> 00:21:35.359
no matter what happens in the future,
I'll always be there for you.

00:21:35.359 --> 00:21:38.305
I promise I'll take care of you
for the rest of my life.

00:21:47.000 --> 00:21:48.519
Don't worry.

00:21:48.519 --> 00:21:51.880
I can handle my own problems, myself.

00:21:51.880 --> 00:21:54.319
You've already helped me more than enough.

00:21:54.319 --> 00:21:58.599
Helping me for a lifetime,
that's too much to ask.

00:22:06.240 --> 00:22:08.640
It's no trouble at all.

00:22:08.640 --> 00:22:10.800
I do it because I want to.

00:22:11.920 --> 00:22:14.400
Besides, didn't you say it yourself?

00:22:14.400 --> 00:22:16.480
"Love is to always feel indebted."

00:22:16.480 --> 00:22:18.879
I feel like I haven't done enough.

00:22:19.519 --> 00:22:22.359
Even blood brothers
have to settle their debts.

00:22:22.359 --> 00:22:24.640
A lifetime...

00:22:24.640 --> 00:22:26.639
is just not realistic.

00:22:30.119 --> 00:22:31.783
But...

00:22:32.519 --> 00:22:34.480
I feel like we're more than just...

00:22:34.480 --> 00:22:36.119
That's enough.

00:22:36.119 --> 00:22:38.039
It's getting late.

00:22:38.039 --> 00:22:40.079
You should head back to campus.

00:22:43.519 --> 00:22:45.440
Okay.

00:24:20.279 --> 00:24:22.319
I should have called out to him.

00:24:22.319 --> 00:24:23.880
But I couldn't make a sound.

00:24:23.880 --> 00:24:25.000
[Ke Ke, don't feel bad]

00:24:25.000 --> 00:24:27.640
I should have kept writing in my diary.

00:24:27.640 --> 00:24:30.839
But I couldn't write another word.

00:24:30.839 --> 00:24:33.440
That final barrier...

00:24:33.440 --> 00:24:36.508
Maybe I never should have tried to cross it.

00:24:37.581 --> 00:24:40.582
Since I was doing just fine on my own before,

00:24:41.508 --> 00:24:44.759
I guess I'll just stay that way.

00:24:44.759 --> 00:24:47.240
Chen Ke.

00:24:47.240 --> 00:24:49.280
You can do this.

00:24:55.079 --> 00:24:57.559
So, in the stage of imperialism,

00:24:57.559 --> 00:25:00.559
due to international monopolies
and the uneven economic

00:25:00.559 --> 00:25:03.480
and political development of capitalism,

00:25:03.480 --> 00:25:05.936
the world market further expanded

00:25:05.936 --> 00:25:10.400
and developed into a unified,
all-encompassing world market.

00:25:10.400 --> 00:25:13.759
Now, speaking of world currency,
let's talk about gold.

00:25:13.759 --> 00:25:18.079
As I just mentioned, it can be used
as a general means of purchase.

00:25:18.079 --> 00:25:21.359
- Here. Coffee.
- A general means of payment

00:25:21.359 --> 00:25:24.279
to balance the deficit
in international payments.

00:25:24.279 --> 00:25:26.942
So if you have gold and silver,

00:25:26.942 --> 00:25:30.359
it's basically like having cash on hand.

00:25:31.160 --> 00:25:35.456
- I see that now, many of our students...
- Hey, Yu Lei.

00:25:35.456 --> 00:25:37.640
The topic the teacher was just talking
about hasn't finished.

00:25:37.640 --> 00:25:39.640
And hoarding silver.

00:25:39.640 --> 00:25:42.799
Actually, this is also a form of...

00:25:44.319 --> 00:25:47.000
So, when you get home,
I want you all to review carefully.

00:25:47.000 --> 00:25:49.000
Okay. That's all for today's class.

00:25:49.000 --> 00:25:50.609
Class dismissed.

00:25:51.812 --> 00:25:53.960
What was today's lecture even about?
I didn't understand a thing.

00:25:53.960 --> 00:25:56.382
My hand is killing me.

00:25:58.279 --> 00:26:00.319
Why don't I go to the next class for you?

00:26:00.319 --> 00:26:01.839
I don't have any classes after this anyway.

00:26:01.839 --> 00:26:03.480
You should hurry back and get some sleep.

00:26:03.480 --> 00:26:05.000
Look how exhausted you are.

00:26:05.000 --> 00:26:06.440
I'm fine. I can handle it.

00:26:06.440 --> 00:26:09.000
Chen Ke, why are you trying so hard?

00:26:09.000 --> 00:26:11.640
Someone messing with your schedule
isn't a big deal.

00:26:11.640 --> 00:26:13.799
Last semester's final,
you didn't even show up,

00:26:13.799 --> 00:26:16.296
and the professor still gave you a pass.

00:26:18.079 --> 00:26:20.200
What's that supposed to mean?

00:26:21.437 --> 00:26:22.680
Are you asking for it?

00:26:22.680 --> 00:26:24.119
Alright, alright.

00:26:24.119 --> 00:26:25.962
What rotten luck.

00:26:25.962 --> 00:26:27.359
He's just joking.

00:26:27.359 --> 00:26:28.640
Don't mind him.

00:26:28.640 --> 00:26:30.250
Let's go, let's go.

00:26:33.799 --> 00:26:35.160
He's always so arrogant.

00:26:35.160 --> 00:26:36.920
Acting all superior.

00:26:36.920 --> 00:26:39.905
He must have pissed off everyone in the dorm.

00:26:39.905 --> 00:26:43.519
Otherwise, why would he suddenly move out
and rent a place on his own?

00:26:43.519 --> 00:26:45.720
Just drop it.

00:26:47.839 --> 00:26:50.920
Don't listen to them.
They're just jealous of you.

00:26:50.920 --> 00:26:52.720
It's okay.

00:26:59.099 --> 00:27:02.659
These classes you've chosen
are either obscure and difficult,

00:27:02.659 --> 00:27:05.160
or they require a specialized foundation.

00:27:05.160 --> 00:27:07.559
It's too hard for you to jump in midway.

00:27:07.559 --> 00:27:09.640
Why don't you just drop them
for this semester

00:27:09.640 --> 00:27:11.559
and re-enroll next semester?

00:27:11.559 --> 00:27:12.902
If I do that,

00:27:12.902 --> 00:27:16.079
then I'd really be letting
He Jin get his way.

00:27:19.799 --> 00:27:22.480
But you still need to balance work and rest.

00:27:22.480 --> 00:27:23.960
Let's go on an outing this weekend.

00:27:23.960 --> 00:27:25.240
You should properly relax.

00:27:25.240 --> 00:27:26.559
I've already got it all planned.

00:27:26.559 --> 00:27:29.319
- We can go to that...
- No, thanks.

00:27:29.319 --> 00:27:30.599
I have classes this weekend.

00:27:30.599 --> 00:27:33.319
If you want to have fun,
you should go by yourself.

00:27:33.920 --> 00:27:35.799
Then let's go to karaoke.

00:27:35.799 --> 00:27:38.000
Or, we could check out a music store.

00:27:38.000 --> 00:27:41.519
There's this new singer called Jay Chou.
His music is pretty good.

00:27:41.519 --> 00:27:43.920
Or, we could go play some pool.

00:27:43.920 --> 00:27:45.519
Bowling would be fun too.

00:27:45.519 --> 00:27:46.920
Yu Lei.

00:27:46.920 --> 00:27:49.519
I have too much on my mind lately.

00:27:49.519 --> 00:27:50.720
My head's a mess.

00:27:50.720 --> 00:27:52.160
And I don't have time to have fun.

00:27:52.160 --> 00:27:54.646
Just leave me alone for now. Okay?

00:27:55.599 --> 00:27:57.559
Okay.

00:28:20.880 --> 00:28:21.920
Chen Ke.

00:28:21.920 --> 00:28:23.839
Professor Meng.
Sorry to bother you again.

00:28:23.839 --> 00:28:26.319
Not at all. Come, have a seat.

00:28:26.960 --> 00:28:30.720
Lately, it seems like something's
been on your mind again.

00:28:32.100 --> 00:28:34.680
About your situation,
I've heard all about it.

00:28:34.680 --> 00:28:38.680
Going on like this must be
really hard on you.

00:28:38.680 --> 00:28:40.000
I have a suggestion.

00:28:40.000 --> 00:28:41.800
Take a look at this.

00:28:44.799 --> 00:28:46.709
[Student Exchange Program]

00:29:18.440 --> 00:29:20.440
Chen Ke, you...

00:29:20.440 --> 00:29:23.000
- Sis.
- All you care about is Chen Ke.

00:29:23.000 --> 00:29:25.186
You don't even want to see me anymore.

00:29:27.577 --> 00:29:29.720
That's not true.

00:29:31.119 --> 00:29:34.400
About Chen Ke's situation,
I've heard all about it.

00:29:34.400 --> 00:29:35.880
I'm really sorry.

00:29:35.880 --> 00:29:37.920
I've been so busy with my own things lately,

00:29:37.920 --> 00:29:39.720
I wasn't able to help much.

00:29:39.720 --> 00:29:41.400
It's fine.

00:29:41.400 --> 00:29:43.079
It's all over now anyway.

00:29:43.079 --> 00:29:44.599
Saves me the trouble of coming to you,

00:29:44.599 --> 00:29:48.599
and having people say I'm pulling strings
or using connections.

00:29:49.920 --> 00:29:51.799
I'm glad it's resolved.

00:29:51.799 --> 00:29:54.400
And, from now on,

00:29:54.400 --> 00:29:57.440
no one will have the chance
to say that about you again.

00:29:59.189 --> 00:30:03.270
Sis, what do you mean?

00:30:04.720 --> 00:30:07.799
I signed up for the school's
study abroad exchange program.

00:30:07.799 --> 00:30:10.680
Starting next semester,
I won't be here anymore.

00:30:10.680 --> 00:30:12.000
What?

00:30:12.000 --> 00:30:14.040
You're going abroad?

00:30:14.799 --> 00:30:15.920
I can't believe it.

00:30:15.920 --> 00:30:18.119
Why are you leaving so soon?

00:30:18.119 --> 00:30:20.799
What's with the sigh? I haven't left yet.

00:30:20.799 --> 00:30:23.079
The paperwork still takes time.

00:30:23.079 --> 00:30:25.920
So, when are you leaving?

00:30:25.920 --> 00:30:28.799
Probably... in about two months.

00:30:28.799 --> 00:30:32.639
I'll go over there first
to get used to the environment.

00:30:35.851 --> 00:30:37.799
Chen Ke.

00:30:37.799 --> 00:30:40.400
Senior. I heard you're going abroad soon.

00:30:40.400 --> 00:30:42.279
I didn't know what gift to get you,

00:30:42.279 --> 00:30:44.079
so I just bought you these flowers.

00:30:44.079 --> 00:30:45.738
Thank you.

00:30:46.799 --> 00:30:48.359
Chen Ke. Come.

00:30:48.359 --> 00:30:50.200
Come sit over here.

00:30:56.519 --> 00:30:58.279
Alright, everyone.

00:30:58.279 --> 00:31:01.359
Even though I won't be here next semester,

00:31:01.359 --> 00:31:05.079
this doesn't have to be
our last get-together. Right?

00:31:05.079 --> 00:31:07.720
I just feel that while I'm still young,

00:31:07.720 --> 00:31:09.599
I want to get out there and travel,
see things,

00:31:09.599 --> 00:31:10.920
and broaden my horizons.

00:31:10.920 --> 00:31:13.960
Who knows,
after I've seen and experienced it all,

00:31:13.960 --> 00:31:17.160
I might find out that
this is the best place after all.

00:31:17.160 --> 00:31:19.119
- Definitely.
- For sure.

00:31:19.119 --> 00:31:22.880
But, when I first got my acceptance letter,

00:31:22.880 --> 00:31:24.920
I was actually a little sad.

00:31:24.920 --> 00:31:27.599
Because I really don't want to leave you all.

00:31:27.599 --> 00:31:32.240
I haven't even left yet,
and I already miss you.

00:31:32.240 --> 00:31:33.920
Don't think I'm being preachy,

00:31:33.920 --> 00:31:37.000
but while we're still young,
and while we're still together,

00:31:37.000 --> 00:31:40.680
we should cherish the good times.

00:31:40.680 --> 00:31:43.240
Cherish the people around us.

00:31:43.240 --> 00:31:45.000
Absolutely. Come on.
To cherishing the people around us.

00:31:45.000 --> 00:31:46.440
- Let's drink to that.
- Let's all toast together.

00:31:46.440 --> 00:31:47.599
- Together.
- Come on, come on.

00:31:47.599 --> 00:31:49.160
Come on, let's drink.

00:31:49.160 --> 00:31:51.640
- Here. Cheers!
- Cheers!

00:31:51.640 --> 00:31:52.839
Cheers!

00:31:52.839 --> 00:31:54.402
Bottoms up!

00:31:55.720 --> 00:31:57.738
- Great booze.
- Bottoms up.

00:32:02.880 --> 00:32:05.279
Come on, everyone.
Let's all take a group photo.

00:32:05.279 --> 00:32:06.640
- Come on. Let's get a shot.
- Come on.

00:32:06.640 --> 00:32:08.039
Everyone ready?

00:32:08.039 --> 00:32:09.720
Three. Two. One.

00:32:09.720 --> 00:32:12.440
Cheese!

00:32:16.920 --> 00:32:18.759
Yu Lei.

00:32:18.759 --> 00:32:21.079
Look at you.
You can barely walk straight.

00:32:21.079 --> 00:32:23.313
And you still insisted on walking me home.

00:32:24.519 --> 00:32:26.720
This is perfect, isn't it?

00:32:26.720 --> 00:32:29.639
We can take a walk and sober up.

00:32:32.359 --> 00:32:36.139
So... how have your classes been lately?

00:32:37.288 --> 00:32:39.279
They're okay.

00:32:39.279 --> 00:32:41.720
I've finally caught up.

00:32:42.440 --> 00:32:44.038
That's good.

00:32:49.400 --> 00:32:52.061
Back during winter break,

00:32:52.061 --> 00:32:55.079
I heard my cousin say
she wanted to go abroad.

00:32:55.079 --> 00:32:59.279
I just didn't expect
she'd be leaving so soon.

00:32:59.279 --> 00:33:01.159
If I had known,

00:33:02.119 --> 00:33:05.000
I would've spent more time with her.

00:33:05.000 --> 00:33:08.440
You can't live your life with "what ifs".

00:33:08.440 --> 00:33:12.000
If you'd spent a little less time
thinking about me,

00:33:12.000 --> 00:33:15.879
maybe you could have
spent more time with your sister.

00:33:17.000 --> 00:33:18.799
No. That's not it.

00:33:18.799 --> 00:33:20.559
What are you talking about?

00:33:20.559 --> 00:33:23.148
How are those two things the same?

00:33:24.534 --> 00:33:26.867
But that's just how it is.

00:33:27.640 --> 00:33:30.559
You can only focus your heart
on one thing at a time.

00:33:30.559 --> 00:33:32.440
If you give more to one,

00:33:32.440 --> 00:33:35.119
you'll naturally have less for the other.

00:33:35.119 --> 00:33:38.480
No one has the energy
to focus on two things at once.

00:33:39.164 --> 00:33:41.079
She's my cousin.

00:33:41.079 --> 00:33:44.400
No matter what happens between us,
we'll always have our family bond.

00:33:44.400 --> 00:33:46.160
But you're different.

00:33:46.160 --> 00:33:47.626
You...

00:33:49.079 --> 00:33:51.759
What's between you and me...

00:33:51.759 --> 00:33:54.399
is a different kind of feeling.

00:33:57.039 --> 00:34:02.472
Yu Lei, maybe I'll be the next one
to go abroad.

00:34:04.799 --> 00:34:07.160
What?

00:34:07.160 --> 00:34:09.479
You're going abroad too?

00:34:10.920 --> 00:34:12.039
Chen Ke.

00:34:12.039 --> 00:34:16.519
The way you're rushing to catch up on credits
is just too much for you.

00:34:16.519 --> 00:34:22.239
So, I'd like to recommend you for the next
student exchange program.

00:34:22.239 --> 00:34:25.759
That way, you can not only secure
your current credits,

00:34:25.759 --> 00:34:27.480
but also broaden your horizons.

00:34:27.480 --> 00:34:31.760
You'll also be able to focus
on your academic growth.

00:34:31.760 --> 00:34:33.959
It's the best of both worlds.

00:34:35.119 --> 00:34:37.679
Professor Meng, am I really good enough?

00:34:37.679 --> 00:34:39.839
Of course you are.

00:34:40.559 --> 00:34:44.400
I know your academic performance
better than anyone.

00:34:44.400 --> 00:34:47.360
And you don't have to worry
about adjusting to the environment.

00:34:47.360 --> 00:34:51.119
The university there
is our school's sister school.

00:34:51.119 --> 00:34:53.012
It has a great academic atmosphere.

00:34:53.012 --> 00:34:56.000
You'll be able to focus on your studies there
without any worries.

00:34:56.000 --> 00:34:57.920
If I change to a new environment,

00:34:57.920 --> 00:35:00.079
I'd probably have to start all over again.

00:35:00.079 --> 00:35:01.159
What's wrong?

00:35:01.159 --> 00:35:03.760
Are you scared?

00:35:03.760 --> 00:35:05.360
I'm not scared.

00:35:05.360 --> 00:35:07.159
It's just...

00:35:07.159 --> 00:35:11.120
Is it that here,
there are ties you can't let go of?

00:35:12.039 --> 00:35:13.239
What?

00:35:13.239 --> 00:35:15.480
There's an opportunity like this?

00:35:15.480 --> 00:35:17.480
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

00:35:17.480 --> 00:35:18.880
I'm going to apply too.

00:35:18.880 --> 00:35:20.800
I want to go abroad with you.

00:35:20.800 --> 00:35:24.679
I'm going abroad
because I agree with Professor Meng.

00:35:24.679 --> 00:35:27.800
I want to further my studies overseas.

00:35:27.800 --> 00:35:29.760
So what's your reason?

00:35:30.400 --> 00:35:34.280
I... I...

00:35:35.280 --> 00:35:36.920
Didn't my cousin say it?

00:35:36.920 --> 00:35:39.920
We should see more of the world
while we're still young.

00:35:39.920 --> 00:35:42.639
Besides, isn't this perfect?

00:35:42.639 --> 00:35:45.879
The two of us can go together
and look out for each other.

00:35:48.840 --> 00:35:51.920
Wait. What do you mean by that?

00:35:51.920 --> 00:35:54.560
Don't you want us to go together?

00:36:00.519 --> 00:36:08.240
I'm so grateful to have
met a friend like you.

00:36:09.320 --> 00:36:13.360
But haven't you realized?

00:36:13.360 --> 00:36:15.481
Ever since you met me,

00:36:15.481 --> 00:36:19.240
you've run into nothing but trouble.

00:36:19.960 --> 00:36:23.360
I think from now on,

00:36:23.360 --> 00:36:25.800
we should give each other some space.

00:36:28.360 --> 00:36:31.360
These past few days, studying by myself,

00:36:31.360 --> 00:36:33.519
I've actually felt at peace.

00:36:33.519 --> 00:36:37.800
And when you're alone,
don't you feel more relaxed too?

00:36:43.880 --> 00:36:45.320
All this time being away from you,

00:36:45.320 --> 00:36:47.680
I haven't been doing well at all.

00:36:49.039 --> 00:36:52.478
Yu Lei, you don't understand.

00:36:54.239 --> 00:36:56.400
My house is just up ahead.

00:36:56.400 --> 00:36:58.289
You can leave me here.

00:36:59.253 --> 00:37:00.890
You should go back.

00:37:03.239 --> 00:37:04.599
No.

00:37:04.599 --> 00:37:05.800
I won't let you.

00:37:05.800 --> 00:37:07.959
I won't let you leave me.

00:37:09.000 --> 00:37:11.920
Yu Lei, you're drunk.

00:37:11.920 --> 00:37:14.159
We can talk tomorrow.

00:37:14.159 --> 00:37:15.280
No, today.

00:37:15.280 --> 00:37:16.679
Right now.

00:37:16.679 --> 00:37:19.600
Don't you know that I...

00:37:33.559 --> 00:37:35.719
I don't know what the future holds.

00:37:35.719 --> 00:37:37.159
The only thing I'm sure of

00:37:37.159 --> 00:37:40.760
is that I want to hold on to him
and never let go.

00:37:40.760 --> 00:37:44.079
I've realized that I've been
in love with you for a long time.

00:37:44.079 --> 00:37:46.400
The kind of "like" that's actually love.

00:37:46.400 --> 00:37:49.239
I can't bear to let you go.

00:37:49.239 --> 00:37:51.800
It seems we were destined to be together.

00:37:51.800 --> 00:37:54.400
You two made my life hell.

00:37:54.400 --> 00:37:56.845
So I'm going to make yours a living hell too!

00:38:00.181 --> 00:38:03.501
Ke Ke... Ke Ke!